column39:
1. The authors should clarify the technical contributions of this paper more clearly;
2. It is better to explain the target order choice for the input of Seq2Seq; 
3. Comparisons between Seq2Seq and some of the mentioned methods are preferred.

Most importantly, I'd like to see
(1) clearer division between the hypothesis that predictive entropy correlates with reading times and the practical ways in which this measure can be calculated;
(2) clearer explanation of Experiments 2 and 3 in particular (which I suspect will be aided by explaining more carefully what the role of the PCFG is in Experiment 1, so that you can point to the differences).
